 {{userName}} 씨!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":3,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main005-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"아, 안녕하세요.\n그런데 무슨 일이야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"어라? 당신들 어디선가 본 적이 있어.\n맞아, 학교! 분명 학교에서 본 것 같은데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main005-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"응, 같은 학교에 같은 학년이잖아.\n……그런데 네가 말하면 정신이 없어지니까\n잠깐만 조용히 해줄래?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"실은 부탁할 게 있어서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"main005-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"……그런 사정으로 라이브 이벤트에 참가해줄\n밴드를 찾고 있어요. 출연이 정해진 건 우리와……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"main005-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"좋아, 참가할게!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main005-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"잠깐, 너무 빨라!\n누가 나오는지도 잘 모르는데……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"누가 나오는지가 상관있는 거야?\n우리는 온 세상을 웃는 얼굴로 채우기 위해 하는 거잖아!\n그렇다면 이렇게 즐거울 것 같은 이벤트는 참가해야지!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main005-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"셰익스피어는 이렇게 말했다.\n「행동이 곧 웅변이다」…… 즉, 그런 거다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"main005-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"카오루 씨, 멋져……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"main005-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"아~ 네. 알았어요! 그렇죠. 그렇습니다.\n저기! 뭐…… 거기 있는 스태프분도 나쁜 사람처럼 안 보이고?\n토야마 씨랑 우시고메 씨도 있으니 괜찮지…… 않으려나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"해냈다! 다들 고마워!\n그런데 이 밴드 이름은 뭐야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":3,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main005-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"헬로……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"헬로 해피월드! 야!\n온 세상을 웃는 얼굴로!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main005-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"……네, 지금 말한 게 다예요.\n일단 소개하자면 보컬은 이 녀석. 츠루마키 코코로.\n기타는 여기 왕자님. 세타 카오루 씨.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"베이스는 같은 학교에 다니는 키타자와 하구미, 드럼은 마츠바라 카논 씨.\n카논 씨는 하나사키가와 2학년이야.\n그리고 나라고 해야 하나? 이 곰은 미셸, DJ.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"많은 연기자가 모인 큰 무대에서 나에게 왕자를 연기하라는 말이더냐.\n과연 흥미롭구나.\n그러면 그 역할, 제대로 연기해 보도록 할까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"main005-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"여러 밴드랑 함께 연주하는 거, 즐거울 거 같아!\n합동 라이브, 합동 라이브!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"main005-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"여러 밴드가 나온다면\n평소보다 긴장될 것 같지만……\n저도 힘낼게요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"main005-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"그런 이유로…… 저기 {{userName}} 씨?\n잘 부탁드릴게요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"main005-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"미사키 짱, 잘 부탁해!\n다음에 밴드끼리 모여서 얼굴 한 번 보고, 연주하는 자리도 만들 거니까\n그때는……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"main005-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"으~~~응! 새로운 만남은 역시 두근거리네!\n더 많이, 더~ 여러 사람을 웃게 할 수 있다고 생각하니까 \n참을 수 없어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motio